flowchart TD
  A[Questionnaire change] --> B{Does the analytical meaning change?}
  B -->|No| C[Keep item_id stable]
  B -->|Maybe| D{Does scoring, dose logic, or factor mapping change?}
  B -->|Yes| E[Create a new dated version and review downstream impact]

  D -->|No| F[Validate navigation and response logic]
  D -->|Yes| E

  C --> G{Is the change only translation or wording?}
  G -->|Yes| H[Usually no factor review]
  G -->|No| I[Check options, required status, and display order]

  E --> Q[Confirm all 11 canonical ASC factors remain complete]
  F --> J[Walk through the survey locally]
  H --> J
  I --> J
  Q --> J

  J --> K[Reload the live questionnaire source only after validation]
  K --> L[Submit once and confirm feedback renders]
